## <a name="new-zealand-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8430">Номер водительского удостоверения Новой Зеландии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8430">New Zealand driver's license number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8431">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации доступен только для использования в:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8431">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8432">Политики предотвращения потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8432">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8433">политики соответствия требованиям к коммуникациям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8433">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8434">управление информацией</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8434">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8435">Управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8435">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8436">Безопасность облачных приложений Майкрософт</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8436">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8437">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8437">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8438">восемь шаблонов альфа-цифр символов</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8438">eight character alphanumeric pattern</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8439">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8439">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8440">восемь шаблонов альфа-цифр символов</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8440">eight character alphanumeric pattern</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8441">две буквы</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8441">two letters</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8442">шесть цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8442">six digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8443">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8443">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8444">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8444">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8445">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8445">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8446">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что этот тип конфиденциальной информации обнаружен, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8446">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8447">Функция Func_newzealand_driver_license_number контента, который соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8447">The function Func_newzealand_driver_license_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8448">Ключевое слово из Keywords_newzealand_driver_license_number найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8448">A keyword from Keywords_newzealand_driver_license_number is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8449">Политика DLP имеет низкую уверенность в том, что этот тип конфиденциальной информации обнаружен, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8449">A DLP policy has low confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8450">Функция Func_newzealand_driver_license_number контента, который соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8450">The function Func_newzealand_driver_license_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- New Zealand Driver License Number -->
      <Entity id="1924b377-d287-49c9-a737-cfe7a8a2615a" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_newzealand_driver_license_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_newzealand_driver_license_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_newzealand_driver_license_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8451">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8451">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_new_zealand_drivers_license_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8452">Keyword_new_zealand_drivers_license_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8452">Keyword_new_zealand_drivers_license_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8453">driverlicence</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8453">driverlicence</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8454">driverlicences</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8454">driverlicences</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8455">lic драйвера</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8455">driver lic</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8456">водительское удостоверение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8456">driver licence</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8457">водительские права</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8457">driver licences</span></span>

## <a name="new-zealand-inland-revenue-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8517">Число внутренних доходов Новой Зеландии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8517">New Zealand inland revenue number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8518">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации доступен только для использования в:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8518">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8519">Политики предотвращения потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8519">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8520">политики соответствия требованиям к коммуникациям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8520">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8521">управление информацией</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8521">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8522">Управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8522">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8523">Безопасность облачных приложений Майкрософт</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8523">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8524">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8524">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8525">восемь или девять цифр с необязательными делимитерами</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8525">eight or nine digits with optional delimiters</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8526">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8526">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8527">восемь или девять цифр с необязательными делимитерами</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8527">eight or nine digits with optional delimiters</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8528">две или три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8528">two or three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8529">необязательный пробел или дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8529">an optional space or hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8530">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8530">three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8531">необязательный пробел или дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8531">an optional space or hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8532">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8532">three digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8533">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8533">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8534">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8534">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8535">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8535">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8536">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что этот тип конфиденциальной информации обнаружен, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8536">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8537">Функция Func_new_zealand_inland_revenue_number контента, который соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8537">The function Func_new_zealand_inland_revenue_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8538">Ключевое слово Keywords_new_zealand_inland_revenue_number найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8538">A keyword from Keywords_new_zealand_inland_revenue_number is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8539">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8539">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8540">Функция Func_new_zealand_inland_revenue_number контента, который соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8540">The function Func_new_zealand_inland_revenue_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- New Zealand Inland Revenue Number -->
      <Entity id="dd0fe2bc-7bcf-455f-bac1-83b1e3eb25fd" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_new_zealand_inland_revenue_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_new_zealand_inland_revenue_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_new_zealand_inland_revenue_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8541">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8541">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_new_zealand_inland_revenue_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8542">Keyword_new_zealand_inland_revenue_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8542">Keyword_new_zealand_inland_revenue_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8543">ird Нет.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8543">ird no.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8545">nz ird</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8545">nz ird</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8546">ird Новой Зеландии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8546">new zealand ird</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8547">ird number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8547">ird number</span></span>

## <a name="new-zealand-ministry-of-health-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8549">Номер министерства здравоохранения Новой Зеландии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8549">New Zealand ministry of health number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8550">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8550">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8551">три буквы, пространство (необязательно) и четыре цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8551">three letters, a space (optional), and four digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8552">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8552">Pattern</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8553">три буквы (не чувствительные к делу), кроме "I" и "O"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8553">three letters (not case-sensitive) except 'I' and 'O'</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8554">пробел (необязательный)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8554">a space (optional)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8555">четыре цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8555">four digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8556">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8556">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8557">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8557">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8558">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8558">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8559">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что этот тип конфиденциальной информации обнаружен, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8559">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8560">функция Func_new_zealand_ministry_of_health_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8560">The function Func_new_zealand_ministry_of_health_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8561">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_nz_terms;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8561">A keyword from Keyword_nz_terms is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8562">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8562">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8563">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8563">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8564">функция Func_new_zealand_ministry_of_health_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8564">The function Func_new_zealand_ministry_of_health_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8565">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8565">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
    <!-- New Zealand Health Number -->
    <Entity id="2b71c1c8-d14e-4430-82dc-fd1ed6bf05c7" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_new_zealand_ministry_of_health_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_nz_terms" />
      </Pattern>
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_new_zealand_ministry_of_health_number" />
       </Pattern>
    </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8566">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8566">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_nz_terms"></a><span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8567">Keyword_nz_terms</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8567">Keyword_nz_terms</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8568">NHI</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8568">NHI</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8569">Новая Зеландия</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8569">New Zealand</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8570">Здравоохранение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8570">Health</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8572">Номер национального индекса здоровья</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8572">National Health Index Number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8573">nhi number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8573">nhi number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8574">nhi нет.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8574">nhi no.</span></span>

## <a name="new-zealand-social-welfare-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8579">Номер социального обеспечения в Новой Зеландии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8579">New Zealand social welfare number</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8580">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации доступен только для использования в:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8580">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8581">Политики предотвращения потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8581">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8582">политики соответствия требованиям к коммуникациям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8582">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8583">управление информацией</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8583">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8584">Управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8584">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8585">Безопасность облачных приложений Майкрософт</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8585">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8586">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8586">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8587">девять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8587">nine digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8588">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8588">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8589">девять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8589">nine digits</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8590">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8590">three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8591">необязательный дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8591">an optional hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8592">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8592">three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8593">необязательный дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8593">an optional hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8594">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8594">three digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8595">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8595">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8596">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8596">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8597">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8597">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8598">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что этот тип конфиденциальной информации обнаружен, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8598">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8599">Функция Func_newzealand_social_welfare_number контент, который соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8599">The function Func_newzealand_social_welfare_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8600">Ключевое слово Keywords_newzealand_social_welfare_number найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8600">A keyword from Keywords_newzealand_social_welfare_number is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8601">Политика DLP имеет низкую уверенность в том, что этот тип конфиденциальной информации обнаружен, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8601">A DLP policy has low confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8602">Функция Func_newzealand_social_welfare_number контент, который соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8602">The function Func_newzealand_social_welfare_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Newzealand Social Welfare Number -->
      <Entity id="20f3c48d-4ac1-4cd2-86bd-34ecc1826e9d" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_newzealand_social_welfare_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_newzealand_social_welfare_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_newzealand_social_welfare_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
    </Version>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8603">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8603">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_new_zealand_social_welfare_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8604">Keyword_new_zealand_social_welfare_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8604">Keyword_new_zealand_social_welfare_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8605">социальное обеспечение #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8605">social welfare #</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8606">социальное обеспечение #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8606">social welfare#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8607">No социального обеспечения.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8607">social welfare No.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8608">номер социального обеспечения</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8608">social welfare number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8609">swn #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8609">swn#</span></span>

   
## <a name="norway-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8610">Идентификационный номер Норвегии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8610">Norway identification number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8611">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8611">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8612">11 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8612">11 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8613">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8613">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8614">11 цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8614">11 digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8615">шесть цифр в формате DDMMYY, которые являются датой рождения</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8615">six digits in the format DDMMYY, which are the date of birth</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8616">трехзначный индивидуальный номер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8616">three-digit individual number</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8617">две контрольные цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8617">two check digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8618">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8618">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8619">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8619">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8620">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8620">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8621">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что этот тип конфиденциальной информации обнаружен, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8621">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8622">функция Func_norway_id_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8622">The function Func_norway_id_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8623">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_norway_id_number;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8623">A keyword from Keyword_norway_id_number is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8624">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8624">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8625">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8625">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8626">функция Func_norway_id_numbe находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8626">The function Func_norway_id_numbe finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8627">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8627">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Norway Identification Number -->
<Entity id="d4c8a798-e9f2-4bd3-9652-500d24080fc3" recommendedConfidence="85" patternsProximity="300">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
     <IdMatch idRef="Func_norway_id_number"/>
     <Match idRef="Keyword_norway_id_number"/>
  </Pattern>
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
     <IdMatch idRef="Func_norway_id_number"/>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8628">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8628">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_norway_id_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8629">Keyword_norway_id_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8629">Keyword_norway_id_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8630">Personal identification number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8630">Personal identification number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8631">Norwegian ID Number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8631">Norwegian ID Number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8632">ID Number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8632">ID Number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8633">Идентификация</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8633">Identification</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8634">Personnummer</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8634">Personnummer</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8635">Fødselsnummer</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8635">Fødselsnummer</span></span>

   
## <a name="philippines-unified-multi-purpose-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8636">Филиппины единый многоцелевой идентификационный номер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8636">Philippines unified multi-purpose identification number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8637">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8637">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8638">12 цифр, разделенных дефисами.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8638">12 digits separated by hyphens</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8639">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8639">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8640">12 цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8640">12 digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8641">четыре цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8641">four digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8642">дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8642">a hyphen</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8643">семь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8643">seven digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8644">дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8644">a hyphen</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8645">одна цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8645">one digit</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8646">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8646">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8647">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8647">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8648">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8648">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8649">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8649">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8650">регулярное выражение Regex_philippines_unified_id находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8650">The regular expression Regex_philippines_unified_id finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8651">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_philippines_id.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8651">A keyword from Keyword_philippines_id is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Philippines Unified Multi-Purpose ID number -->
<Entity id="019b39dd-8c25-4765-91a3-d9c6baf3c3b3" recommendedConfidence="75" patternsProximity="300">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
     <IdMatch idRef="Regex_philippines_unified_id"/>
     <Match idRef="Keyword_philippines_id"/>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8652">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8652">Keywords</span></span>
   
#### <a name="keyword_philippines_id"></a><span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8653">Keyword_philippines_id</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8653">Keyword_philippines_id</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8654">Unified Multi-Purpose ID</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8654">Unified Multi-Purpose ID</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8655">UMID</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8655">UMID</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8656">Identity Card</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8656">Identity Card</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8657">Pinag-isang Multi-Layunin ID</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8657">Pinag-isang Multi-Layunin ID</span></span>

## <a name="poland-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8658">Номер водительских прав в Польше</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8658">Poland driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8659">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8659">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8660">14 цифр, содержащих две косые черты</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8660">14 digits containing two forward slashes</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8661">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8661">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8662">14 цифр и две косые черты:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8662">14 digits and two forward slashes:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8663">пять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8663">five digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8664">перенарезаемая косая черта</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8664">a forward slash</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8665">две цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8665">two digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8666">перенарезаемая косая черта</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8666">a forward slash</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8667">семь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8667">seven digits</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8668">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8668">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8669">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8669">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8670">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8670">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8671">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8671">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8672">Обычное выражение  `Regex_poland_eu_driver's_license_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8672">The regular expression  `Regex_poland_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8673">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` из `Keywords_poland_eu_driver's_license_number` или найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8673">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` or `Keywords_poland_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Poland Driver's License Number -->
      <Entity id="24d51f99-ee9e-4060-a077-cae58cab1ee4" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_poland_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_poland_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8798">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8798">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8799">три буквы и шесть цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8799">three letters and six digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8800">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8800">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8801">три буквы (не чувствительные к делу) с последующим шестью цифрами</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8801">three letters (not case-sensitive) followed by six digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8802">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8802">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8803">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8803">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8804">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8804">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8805">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8805">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8806">функция Func_polish_national_id находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8806">The function Func_polish_national_id finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8807">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_polish_national_id_passport_number;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8807">A keyword from Keyword_polish_national_id_passport_number is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8808">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8808">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Poland Identity Card-->
<Entity id="25E64989-ED5D-40CA-A939-6C14183BB7BF" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_polish_national_id" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_polish_national_id_passport_number" />
      </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

- <span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8811">Особист dowód</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8811">Dowód osobisty</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8812">Numer dowodu osobistego</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8812">Numer dowodu osobistego</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8813">Nazwa i numer dowodu osobistego</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8813">Nazwa i numer dowodu osobistego</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8814">Nazwa i nr dowodu osobistego</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8814">Nazwa i nr dowodu osobistego</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8815">Nazwa i nr dowodu tożsamości</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8815">Nazwa i nr dowodu tożsamości</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8816">Dowód Tożsamości</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8816">Dowód Tożsamości</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="61ebb-p145">dow. os.
</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-p145">dow. os.</span></span>

   
## <a name="poland-national-id-pesel"></a><span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8819">Польский национальный ID (PESEL)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8819">Poland national ID (PESEL)</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8820">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8820">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8821">11 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8821">11 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8822">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8822">Pattern</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8823">шесть цифр, представляющих дату рождения в формате YYMMDD</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8823">six digits representing date of birth in the format YYMMDD</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8824">четыре цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8824">four digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8825">одна контрольная цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8825">one check digit</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8826">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8826">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8827">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8827">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8828">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8828">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8829">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что этот тип конфиденциальной информации обнаружен, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8829">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8830">функция Func_pesel_identification_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8830">The function Func_pesel_identification_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8831">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_pesel_identification_number;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8831">A keyword from Keyword_pesel_identification_number is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8832">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8832">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8833">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8833">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8834">функция Func_pesel_identification_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8834">The function Func_pesel_identification_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8835">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8835">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Poland National ID (PESEL) -->
      <Entity id="E3AAF206-4297-412F-9E06-BA8487E22456" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_pesel_identification_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_pesel_identification_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_pesel_identification_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8836">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8836">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_pesel_identification_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8837">Keyword_pesel_identification_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8837">Keyword_pesel_identification_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8839">dowódosobisty</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8839">dowódosobisty</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8840">niepowtarzalny numer</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8840">niepowtarzalny numer</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8841">niepowtarzalnynumer</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8841">niepowtarzalnynumer</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8842">nr.-pesel</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8842">nr.-pesel</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8843">nr-pesel</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8843">nr-pesel</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8844">numer identyfikacyjny</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8844">numer identyfikacyjny</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8845">pesel</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8845">pesel</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8846">tożsamości narodowej</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8846">tożsamości narodowej</span></span>

   
## <a name="poland-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8847">Номер паспорта Польши</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8847">Poland passport number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8848">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации входит в тип конфиденциальной информации номера паспорта ЕС.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8848">This sensitive information type entity is included in the EU Passport Number sensitive information type.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8849">Он также доступен в качестве отдельного объекта типа конфиденциальной информации.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8849">It's also available as a stand-alone sensitive information type entity.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8850">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8850">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8851">две буквы и семь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8851">two letters and seven digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8852">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8852">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8853">Две буквы (не чувствительные к делу) с семью цифрами</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8853">Two letters (not case-sensitive) followed by seven digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8854">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8854">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8855">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8855">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8856">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8856">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8857">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что этот тип конфиденциальной информации обнаружен, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8857">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8858">Функция находит `Func_polish_passport_number_v2` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8858">The function `Func_polish_passport_number_v2` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8859">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8859">The checksum passes.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8860">Ключевое слово `Keywords_eu_passport_number` из `Keyword_polish_national_passport_number` или найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8860">A keyword from `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keyword_polish_national_passport_number` is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8861">Найдено ключевое `Keywords_eu_passport_date` слово.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8861">A keyword from `Keywords_eu_passport_date` is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8862">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8862">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8863">Функция находит `Func_polish_passport_number_v2` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8863">The function `Func_polish_passport_number_v2` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8864">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8864">The checksum passes.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8865">Ключевое слово `Keywords_eu_passport_number` из `Keyword_polish_national_passport_number` или найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8865">A keyword from `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keyword_polish_national_passport_number` is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8866">Политика DLP имеет низкую уверенность в том, что этот тип конфиденциальной информации обнаружен, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8866">A DLP policy has low confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8867">Функция находит `Func_polish_passport_number_v2` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8867">The function `Func_polish_passport_number_v2` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8868">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8868">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Poland Passport Number -->
      <Entity id="03937FB5-D2B6-4487-B61F-0F8BFF7C3517" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_polish_passport_number_v2" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_date" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keyword_polish_national_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_polish_passport_number_v2" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keyword_polish_national_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_polish_passport_number_v2" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="poland-regon-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8894">Номер REGON в Польше</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8894">Poland REGON number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8895">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации доступен только для использования в:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8895">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8896">Политики предотвращения потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8896">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8897">политики соответствия требованиям к коммуникациям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8897">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8898">управление информацией</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8898">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8899">Управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8899">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8900">Безопасность облачных приложений Майкрософт</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8900">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8901">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8901">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8902">9-значный или 14-значный номер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8902">9-digit or 14-digit number</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8903">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8903">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8904">девять цифр или 14-значное число:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8904">nine digit or 14-digit number:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8905">девять цифр или</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8905">nine digits or</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8906">девять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8906">nine digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8907">дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8907">hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8908">пять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8908">five digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8909">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8909">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8910">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8910">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8911">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8911">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8912">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что этот тип конфиденциальной информации обнаружен, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8912">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8913">Функция Func_polish_regon_number контента, который соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8913">The function Func_polish_regon_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8914">Ключевое слово Keywords_polish_regon_number найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8914">A keyword from Keywords_polish_regon_number is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8915">Политика DLP имеет низкую уверенность в том, что этот тип конфиденциальной информации обнаружен, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8915">A DLP policy has low confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8916">Функция Func_polish_regon_number контента, который соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8916">The function Func_polish_regon_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Polish REGON Number  -->
      <Entity id="fc87b421-f437-4f8b-b739-29a735ead0d9" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_polish_regon_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_polish_regon_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_polish_regon_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

- <span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8922">статистический нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8922">statistical no</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8923">номер regon</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8923">regon number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8925">regonno #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8925">regonno#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8926">ID компании</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8926">company id</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8927">companyid #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8927">companyid#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8928">companyidno #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8928">companyidno#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8929">numer statystyczny</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8929">numer statystyczny</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8930">regon numeru</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8930">numeru regon</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8931">numerstatystyczny #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8931">numerstatystyczny#</span></span>

## <a name="poland-tax-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8933">Номер налоговой идентификации в Польше</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8933">Poland tax identification number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8934">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации доступен только для использования в:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8934">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8935">Политики предотвращения потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8935">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8936">политики соответствия требованиям к коммуникациям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8936">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8937">управление информацией</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8937">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8938">Управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8938">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8939">Безопасность облачных приложений Майкрософт</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8939">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8940">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8940">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8941">11 цифр без пробелов или делимитеров</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8941">11 digits with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8942">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8942">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8943">11 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8943">11 digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8944">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8944">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8945">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8945">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8946">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8946">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8947">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что этот тип конфиденциальной информации обнаружен, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8947">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8948">Функция находит  `Func_poland_eu_tax_file_number` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8948">The function  `Func_poland_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8949">Найдено ключевое  `Keywords_poland_eu_tax_file_number` слово.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8949">A keyword from  `Keywords_poland_eu_tax_file_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
  
```xml
      <!-- Poland Tax Identification Number -->
      <Entity id="1ff28b4d-40f2-49e9-b677-9606a88e2bca" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_poland_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_poland_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="portugal-citizen-card-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8979">Номер карточки гражданина Португалии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8979">Portugal citizen card number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8980">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8980">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8981">восемь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8981">eight digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8982">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8982">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8983">восемь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8983">eight digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8984">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8984">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8985">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8985">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8986">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8986">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8987">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что этот тип конфиденциальной информации обнаружен, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8987">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8988">регулярное выражение Regex_portugal_citizen_card находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8988">The regular expression Regex_portugal_citizen_card finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="61ebb-8989">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_portugal_citizen_card.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-8989">A keyword from Keyword_portugal_citizen_card is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Portugal Citizen Card Number -->
<Entity id="91a7ece2-add4-4986-9a15-c84544d81ecd" recommendedConfidence="85" patternsProximity="300">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
     <IdMatch idRef="Regex_portugal_citizen_card"/>
     <Match idRef="Keyword_portugal_citizen_card"/>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="portugal-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="61ebb-9009">Номер водительских прав Португалии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-9009">Portugal driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="61ebb-9010">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-9010">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="61ebb-9011">два шаблона : две буквы с 5-8 цифрами со специальными символами</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-9011">two patterns - two letters followed by 5-8 digits with special characters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="61ebb-9012">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-9012">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="61ebb-9013">Шаблон 1. Две буквы, за которыми следуют 5/6 со специальными символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-9013">Pattern 1: Two letters followed by 5/6 with special characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="61ebb-9014">Две буквы (не чувствительные к делу)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-9014">Two letters (not case-sensitive)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="61ebb-9015">дефис;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-9015">A hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="61ebb-9016">Пять или шесть цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-9016">Five or Six digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="61ebb-9017">Пробел</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-9017">A space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="61ebb-9018">Одна цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-9018">One digit</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="61ebb-9019">Шаблон 2. Одна буква с 6/8 цифрами со специальными символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-9019">Pattern 2: One letter followed by 6/8 digits with special characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="61ebb-9020">Одна буква (не деликатная)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-9020">One letter (not case-sensitive)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="61ebb-9021">дефис;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-9021">A hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="61ebb-9022">Шесть или восемь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-9022">Six or eight digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="61ebb-9023">Пробел</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-9023">A space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="61ebb-9024">одна цифра.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-9024">One digit</span></span>

    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="61ebb-9025">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-9025">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="61ebb-9026">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-9026">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="61ebb-9027">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-9027">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="61ebb-9028">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-9028">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="61ebb-9029">Обычное выражение  `Regex_portugal_eu_driver's_license_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-9029">The regular expression  `Regex_portugal_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="61ebb-9030">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` из `Keywords_portugal_eu_driver's_license_number` или найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-9030">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` or `Keywords_portugal_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Portugal Driver's License Number -->
      <Entity id="977f1e5a-2c33-4bcc-b516-95bb275cff23" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_portugal_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_portugal_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="portugal-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="61ebb-9162">Номер паспорта Португалии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-9162">Portugal passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="61ebb-9163">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-9163">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="61ebb-9164">одна буква с шестью цифрами без пробелов или делимитеров</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-9164">one letter followed by six digits with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="61ebb-9165">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-9165">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="61ebb-9166">одна буква с шестью цифрами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-9166">one letter followed by six digits:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="61ebb-9167">одна буква (не деликатная)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-9167">one letter (not case-sensitive)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="61ebb-9168">шесть цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-9168">six digits</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="61ebb-9169">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-9169">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="61ebb-9170">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-9170">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="61ebb-9171">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-9171">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="61ebb-9172">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что этот тип конфиденциальной информации обнаружен, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-9172">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="61ebb-9173">Обычное выражение  `Regex_portugal_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-9173">The regular expression  `Regex_portugal_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="61ebb-9174">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` из `Keywords_portugal_eu_passport_number` или найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-9174">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_portugal_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="61ebb-9175">Обычное выражение `Regex_eu_passport_date1` находит дату в формате DD.MM.YYYYY или ключевое слово `Keywords_eu_passport_date` из</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-9175">The regular expression `Regex_eu_passport_date1` finds date in the format DD.MM.YYYY or a keyword from `Keywords_eu_passport_date` is found</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="61ebb-9176">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-9176">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="61ebb-9177">Обычное выражение  `Regex_portugal_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-9177">The regular expression  `Regex_portugal_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="61ebb-9178">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` из `Keywords_portugal_eu_passport_number` или найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-9178">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_portugal_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span>
    
```xml
      <!-- Portugal Passport Number -->
      <Entity id="080a52fd-a7bc-431e-b54d-51f08f59db11" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_portugal_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_portugal_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Regex_eu_passport_date1" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_date" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_portugal_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_portugal_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="portugal-tax-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="61ebb-9205">Идентификация налога в Португалии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-9205">Portugal tax identification number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="61ebb-9206">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-9206">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="61ebb-9207">девять цифр с необязательными пробелами</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-9207">nine digits with optional spaces</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="61ebb-9208">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-9208">Pattern</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="61ebb-9209">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-9209">three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="61ebb-9210">необязательный пробел</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-9210">an optional space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="61ebb-9211">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-9211">three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="61ebb-9212">необязательный пробел</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-9212">an optional space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="61ebb-9213">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-9213">three digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="61ebb-9214">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-9214">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="61ebb-9215">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-9215">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="61ebb-9216">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-9216">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="61ebb-9217">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что этот тип конфиденциальной информации обнаружен, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-9217">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="61ebb-9218">Функция находит  `Func_portugal_eu_tax_file_number` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-9218">The function  `Func_portugal_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="61ebb-9219">Найдено ключевое  `Keywords_portugal_eu_tax_file_number` слово.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-9219">A keyword from  `Keywords_portugal_eu_tax_file_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="61ebb-9220">Политика DLP имеет низкую уверенность в том, что этот тип конфиденциальной информации обнаружен, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-9220">A DLP policy has low confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="61ebb-9221">Функция находит  `Func_portugal_eu_tax_file_number` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61ebb-9221">The function  `Func_portugal_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Portugal Tax Identification Number -->
      <Entity id="65372402-3131-4f1e-9983-4439841d1f15" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_portugal_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_portugal_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_portugal_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```
